  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc6\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0db1\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Stop the rice mafia",
      "body_lines": [
        "The authorities should intervene to stop the rice flour mafia in the country and impose a control price on rice flour. The. M. Mr. Sanur said.",
        "Mr. Sanur said that a third party was buying wet paddy from farmers at a low price and turning it into rice flour and selling it at a higher price of Rs. 325 per kilo."
      ],
